{"tid":1438271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[做實事] 討論下8月5號後嘅方向","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:29:28.000Z","uid":303210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"164e075885faf59b4b3b0431bc188e490c2c5ac9","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"呢個Post係響應返咁多位手足開始提出，唔好再推恥笑Post、起罵戰、分化、割蓆嘅等等等等，對於個運動發展、行落去無幫助嘅Post嘅。<br />\n<br />\n帶個頭盔先，呢個Post係集中所有手足、智囊，用黎分析現況嘅。<br />\n<br />\n我自己發表下先:<br />\n<br />\n其實打從8月5號三罷未開始都好，我都覺得只係罷一日係完全無作為的，因為都只係當打左一日風，對政府嘅壓力有限，係罷就至少罷一個禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n其次係，罷工參與人數唔算多。唔知係我大貪定乜嘢，我覺得只係得35萬人參與嘅呢個數目係一啲都唔值得用黎打J。<br />\n<br />\n第三，時間緊迫了。已經8月上旬，只要到左9月開學，運動嘅摩打將會大大大大大大咁慢落黎，到時就真係GG。<br />\n<br />\n基於第一、二個Point，我認為一定要以誓必令到罷工時間，參與人數大大咁增加為大前提之下，藴釀下次罷工。而呢一個行動先於一切。<br />\n<br />\n承接上一段兼回應Point 3，所以蘊釀嘅時間必需要快了，在9月前發生多一次，務求激起千重浪！<br />\n<br />\n我只係好不負責任咁講左一啲諗法，唔知各位手足點睇？另外就係，各位手足除左可以討論一下我提及嘅嘢嘅可能性外，當然亦都可以開展其他關於方向、行動嘅brain storming。我開呢個Post始終都係想拉返各位手足返黎要做&ldquo;實事喇&rdquo;呢個空間到！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0894ece7cef8253009eb77ff0f29a54dd0c311a3","tid":1438271,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><ins>不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDWLJC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDWLJC7.jpg&h=198dc984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ediuqRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FediuqRs.jpg&h=cef45c59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnOREbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnOREbt.jpg&h=38a4798d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ABLJC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ABLJC8.jpg&h=2275940b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPc7cwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPc7cwu.jpg&h=59d9830a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PawPqRu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPawPqRu.png&h=55bed97d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3F1gYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3F1gYa.jpg&h=be326d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VdVmpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VdVmpQ.jpg&h=b8c26886&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ec9cd4f4ba5c777749ed20f7fd2c4c278d7f963","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"推下先！<br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘢了！"},{"pid":"4395eceaf6e239349aee91e5cf89f05f24899ce4","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"再推！！！"},{"pid":"4176682072c8fd805b12b6d78453a65c2f73c179","tid":1438271,"uid":276674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4395eceaf6e239349aee91e5cf89f05f24899ce4","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"再推！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf3314194b48bd461db65e68b565c69e268c3146","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"又推！！！！"},{"pid":"e17c0d253a28fa7b93725ee8929ed722da73d628","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"Push！！！！"},{"pid":"d1ea1cee2f5ecca04ecfa67b06e20feb5e958763","tid":1438271,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:42:42.000Z","msg":"推啊推！！！"},{"pid":"e47